      "content": "hey so i work in data entry at this big finance firm and lately i've been looking at the patterns in the spreadsheets i'm inputting. it feels way bigger than just numbers. like it's almost like i'm seeing the blueprints for some kind of massive shift in how the whole global economy works. i feel like nobody else in my office even realizes what's actually happening. do you think it's possible the management knows this and is just keeping us in the dark about the real scale of it?",
